WEBVTT

00:00:22.530 --> 00:00:26.430
I HAD MY APPENDIX OUT
WHEN I WAS TEN

00:00:26.430 --> 00:00:28.830
AND I REMEMBER THAT
THEY GAVE YOU ETHER THEN

00:00:28.830 --> 00:00:33.730
AND I REMEMBER THE FEELING
OF FLOATING OFF UNDER THE ETHER

00:00:33.730 --> 00:00:36.070
AND I LOVED THAT FEELING.

00:00:36.070 --> 00:00:40.430
IT WAS JUST LIKE BEING
LIFTED OUT OF MY MIND

00:00:40.430 --> 00:00:42.270
IN A VERY NICE WAY
BECAUSE MY MIND

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:44.530
WASN'T A VERY GOOD
NEIGHBORHOOD FOR ME TO BE IN.

00:00:44.530 --> 00:00:46.200
I WASN'T VERY SAFE THERE.

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.530
YOU KNOW, THE SCENARIO

00:00:47.530 --> 00:00:49.830
IS THAT YOU START SMOKING POT,
DRINKING BEER

00:00:49.830 --> 00:00:51.470
THEN YOU GO TO THE HARD DRUGS.

00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.430
I WENT STRAIGHT
TO A SPIKE IN MY ARM.

00:00:53.430 --> 00:00:54.870
I AM THE KIND OF PERSON

00:00:54.870 --> 00:00:57.700
WHO WANTS TO JUST DO IT
AND DO IT AND DO IT AND DO IT.

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:01.900
YOU KNOW... "HIS EYES ARE BIGGER
THAN HIS STOMACH" SORT OF THING.

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:04.630
YOU KNOW, I COULDN'T
POSSIBLY BE ADDICTED TO DRUGS.

00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:06.600
I WAS A POLICE OFFICER
DOING MY JOB.

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:08.670
I WAS USING TWO,
THREE TIMES A WEEK

00:01:08.670 --> 00:01:11.470
THEN EVERY EVENING,
AND THEN ALL WEEKEND LONG.

00:01:11.470 --> 00:01:18.000
IN FACT, OF A GROUP OF
ABOUT 40 OF US LIVELY, ROBUST

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.500
HEALTHY, INTELLIGENT,
BEAUTIFUL YOUNGSTERS

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:23.570
I THINK I'M PROBABLY
THE LAST ONE ALIVE.

