YOU KNOW, GETTING... GETTING UP
AT 5:00 IN THE MORNING

00:47:28.370 --> 00:47:29.970
AND RUNNING AND DOING PUSHUPS

00:47:29.970 --> 00:47:32.400
AND THAT KIND OF THING
DURING BASIC TRAINING.

00:47:32.400 --> 00:47:33.900
I... THAT WAS VERY HELPFUL.

00:47:33.900 --> 00:47:37.700
AND, UM... AND I THINK THAT GAVE
ME A BIT OF A... A GRIP.

00:47:37.700 --> 00:47:40.370
IT GOT ME BACK INTO
MY OLD PHYSICAL SELF

00:47:40.370 --> 00:47:44.530
WHERE... YOU KNOW, I COULD... I
COULD START TO FEEL GOOD AGAIN

00:47:44.530 --> 00:47:48.070
FEEL PHYSICALLY GOOD,
BECAUSE THE DRUGS RUN YOU DOWN

00:47:48.070 --> 00:47:51.670
YOU KNOW, THEY RUN... RUN
YOUR BODY DOWN TERRIBLY.

