AND I ONLY STOPPED
BECAUSE IT WAS... TO ME...

00:48:06.870 --> 00:48:09.470
FROM MY POINT OF VIEW,
IT WAS EITHER STOP OR DIE.

00:48:09.470 --> 00:48:11.900
AND SO I PREFERRED
THE ALTERNATIVE OF LIVING

00:48:11.900 --> 00:48:13.530
AND SO I STOPPED.

