I DON'T KNOW WHAT MADE ME WAKE
UP ONE DAY AND SAY, "THIS IS IT.

00:48:18.600 --> 00:48:21.630
I CAN'T TAKE ANOTHER
MINUTE OF THIS."

00:48:21.630 --> 00:48:24.300
BUT ONCE I GOT GOING
IN RECOVERY

00:48:24.300 --> 00:48:26.430
I KNEW THAT I HAD TO PRAY.

