I KNEW THAT I HAD TO FIND, UM,
A GOD THAT I COULD BELIEVE IN.

00:48:31.600 --> 00:48:35.770
I KNEW THAT I... THAT
I COULDN'T DO IT ON MY OWN.

00:48:35.770 --> 00:48:42.400
AND, UM, I... BELIEVE THAT
THERE IS SOME SPIRIT WITHIN ME

00:48:42.400 --> 00:48:44.800
THAT IS MY STRENGTH.

00:48:44.800 --> 00:48:49.730
THE POWER CAN BE...
WHATEVER YOU WANT IT TO BE

00:48:49.730 --> 00:48:52.370
SO LONG AS IT AIN'T YOU.

